%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Born%20In%20India%2C%20Now%20In%20Pakistan%3A%20Indian%20Heart%20Gives%20Pak%20Girl%20New%20Life%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Indian%20heart%20has%20given%20new%20life%20to%20a%20young%20woman%20from%20Karachi%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20her%20family%2C%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fheart-transplant-surgery%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etransplant%20surgery%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Chennai's%20MGM%20Healthcare.%20And%20that%20is%20only%20half%20of%20this%20remarkable%20story%3B%20the%20surgeons%2C%20and%20the%20hospital%2C%20performed%20the%20procedure%20free%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20medical%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E19-year-old%20Ayesha%20Rashan%2C%20the%20transplant%20recipient%2C%20wants%20to%20study%20fashion%20design.%20Her%20family%20said%20they%20could%20not%20have%20afforded%20the%20operation%20without%20the%20support%20of%20the%20trust%20and%20the%20Chennai%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20good%20after%20the%20transplant%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Rashan%20told%20NDTV%20as%20her%20mother%20thanked%20the%20doctors%2C%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20the%20medical%20trust.%20Ms%20Rashan's%20condition%20is%20stable%2C%20and%20she%20can%20return%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20doctors%2C%20Ms%20Rashan%20was%20admitted%20with%20severe%20heart%20dysfunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20heart%20failure%2C%20she%20was%20put%20on%20ECMO%2C%20which%20is%20a%20form%20of%20life%20support%20for%20people%20with%20life-threatening%20illness%20or%20injury%20that%20affects%20the%20function%20of%20their%20heart%20or%20lungs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20her%20heart%20pump%20then%20developed%20a%20leak%20in%20a%20valve%2C%20necessitating%20a%20full%20heart%20transplant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20heart%20transplant%20can%20cost%20over%20Rs%2035%20lakh.%20In%20Ms%20Rashan's%20case%2C%20this%20bill%20was%20covered%20by%20the%20doctors%20and%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20donor%20heart%20came%20from%20Delhi%2C%20and%20the%20young%20girl%20was%20lucky%2C%20Dr%20KR%20Balakrishnan%2C%20Director%20(Heart%20and%20Lung%20Transplant)%2C%20and%20Dr%20Suresh%20Rao%20(Co-Director%20(Heart%20and%20Lung%20Transplant)%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20Ms%20Rashan%20received%20the%20heart%20rapidly%20since%20there%20were%20no%20competing%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20is%20like%20my%20daughter...%20every%20life%20matters%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctors%20said%2C%20underlining%20Chennai's%20status%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcapital%20of%20organ%20donation%20and%20transplant%20surgery%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctors%20also%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20fellow%20professionals%20and%20hospitals%20in%20other%20states%2C%20saying%20in%20several%20cases%20viable%20organs%20were%20being%20discarded%20because%20of%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20transplant%20surgery%2C%20which%20cannot%20be%20afforded%20by%20most%20people%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftake-action-against-hospitals-involved-in-illegal-transplant-centre-to-states-5490893%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAct%20Against%20Hospitals%20Involved%20In%20Illegal%20Transplant%2C%20States%20Told%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20high%20costs%20make%20transplant%20surgeries%20a%20rich%20field%20of%20opportunities%20for%20criminals%2C%20and%2C%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20the%20central%20government%20this%20week%20asked%20all%20states%20and%20UTs%20to%20investigate%20all%20possible%20violations%20and%20take%20action%2C%20including%20suspending%20licenses%20of%20hospitals%20that%20perform%20illegal%20transplants.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713963120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fq36ssc7_indian-heart-pakistan-girl-transplant_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fchennai-mgm-healthcare-indian-heart-in-pakistan-girl-born-in-india-now-in-pakistan-indian-heart-gives-pak-girl-new-life-5513778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20Indian%20heart%20has%20given%20new%20life%20to%20a%20young%20woman%20from%20Karachi%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20her%20family%2C%20after%20a%20transplant%20surgery%20at%20Chennai's%20MGM%20Healthcare.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fchennai-mgm-healthcare-indian-heart-in-pakistan-girl-born-in-india-now-in-pakistan-indian-heart-gives-pak-girl-new-life-5513778%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fchennai-mgm-healthcare-indian-heart-in-pakistan-girl-born-in-india-now-in-pakistan-indian-heart-gives-pak-girl-new-life-5513778%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsouth%2Fchennai-mgm-healthcare-indian-heart-in-pakistan-girl-born-in-india-now-in-pakistan-indian-heart-gives-pak-girl-new-life-5513778%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Urges%20Voters%20Not%20To%20Vote%20For%20Its%20Own%20Candidate%20In%20This%20Seat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20peculiar%20poll%20battle%20is%20on%20the%20cards%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Banswara-Dungarpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20in%20Rajasthan%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20appealing%20to%20the%20people%20not%20to%20vote%20for%20its%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%3A%20After%20much%20flip-flop%2C%20the%20Congress%20decided%20to%20support%20Bharat%20Adivasi%20Party%20(BAP)%20candidate%20Rajkumar%20Roat%20-%20a%20day%20before%20the%20last%20date%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20nominations%20-%20despite%20fielding%20its%20own%20candidate%20Arvind%20Damor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20accordance%20with%20the%20party's%20announcement%20to%20support%20the%20BAP%2C%20Damor%20was%20supposed%20to%20withdraw%20his%20nomination%20papers%20but%20he%20was%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%20till%20the%20last%20date%20of%20withdrawal%20of%20nominations%20was%20over.%20Later%2C%20appearing%20before%20the%20media%2C%20Damor%20feigned%20ignorance%20about%20the%20developments%20and%20declared%20that%20he%20would%20contest%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20bipolar%20contest%20between%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress-BAP%20alliance%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20three-way%20fight%20with%20Damor%20likely%20to%20divide%20the%20Congress%20votes%20thus%2C%20giving%20an%20edge%20to%20the%20saffron%20party%20candidate%20-%20Mahendrajit%20Singh%20Malviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20local%20leadership%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20appealed%20to%20the%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20Roat%20instead%20of%20their%20own%20candidate%2C%20Damor%20has%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20the%20support%20of%20a%20section%20of%20the%20party%20leaders%20who%20are%20against%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20Bamnia%2C%20a%20district-level%20leader%2C%20and%20the%20son%20of%20Congress%20MLA%20Arjun%20Bamnia%20said%20the%20party%20was%20supporting%20Roat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20stand%20is%20clear%2C%20we%20are%20supporting%20the%20BAP%20candidate.%20We%20are%20working%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people%20and%20the%20directions%20received%20from%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bamnia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20local%20Congress%20leader%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20asking%20people%20clearly%20to%20not%20vote%20for%20the%20Congress%20candidate%20(Damor).%26quot%3B%20Although%20several%20local%20residents%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20that%20the%20contest%20was%20primarily%20between%20Malviya%20and%20Roat%2C%20some%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20Damor's%20refusal%20to%20toe%20the%20party%20line%20was%20embarrassing%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBAP%2C%20which%20was%20established%20in%20southern%20Rajasthan%20ahead%20of%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections%2C%20has%20three%20MLAs%2C%20including%20Roat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanswara-Dungarpur%20is%20a%20reserved%20seat%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20will%20go%20to%20polls%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20addressed%20a%20rally%20in%20Banswara%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20he%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20opposition%20party%20was%20planning%20to%20give%20people's%20hard-earned%20money%20to%20%26quot%3Binfiltrators%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20have%20more%20children%26quot%3B%20and%20referred%20to%20former%20PM%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20speech%20in%202006%20to%20contend%20he%20had%20said%20that%20Muslims%20have%20the%20%26quot%3Bfirst%20claim%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20country's%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20campaigning%20speeches%2C%20Mr%20Malviya%20has%20accused%20Mr%20Roat%20of%20misleading%20the%20people%20of%20Banswara%20while%20he%2C%20in%20return%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20dividing%20the%20tribal%20community%20by%20the%20Congress-BAP%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20will%20these%20people%20take%20our%20tribal%20brothers%20and%20sisters%3F%20They%20are%20misleading%20the%20tribal%20community.%20Building%20a%20house%20for%20one%20person%20does%20not%20benefit%20the%20entire%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Malviya%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20working%20to%20spread%20anarchy.%20No%20matter%20how%20much%20they%20try%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20going%20to%20win%20this%20seat%20by%20lakhs%20of%20votes.%20The%20alliance%20of%20Congress%20and%20BAP%20will%20not%20work.%20It%20only%20shows%20that%20the%20Congress%20did%20not%20get%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20Banswara-Dungarpur%20seat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20him%2C%20Mr%20Raot%20said%20the%20BJP%20candidate%20was%20%26quot%3Bdividing%26quot%3B%20and%20abusing%20the%20tribal%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20kind%20of%20statements%20Malviya%20is%20giving...%20he%20is%20abusing%20the%20tribal%20community.%20The%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20divide%20the%20tribal%20community.%20Our%20tribal%20people%20may%20be%20associated%20with%20any%20party%2C%20be%20it%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20Congress%2C%20but%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20unite%20them.%20We%20think%20above%20the%20party%2C%20we%20think%20for%20the%20tribal%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Damor%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20a%20faction%20of%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20was%20against%20the%20alliance%20with%20BAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20support%20from%20the%20people%20and%20the%20party%20leaders%20who%20are%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20alliance.%20I%20am%20confident%20of%20winning%20the%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Damor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20BJP%20state%20president%20Satish%20Poonia%2C%20who%20campaigned%20in%20the%20constituency%20in%20support%20of%20Malviya%2C%20said%20that%20Congress%20was%20nowhere%20in%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20condition%20of%20Congress%20leaders%20has%20become%20such%20that%20when%20they%20went%20to%20a%20'bhandara'%2C%20the%20'prasad'%20was%20over%20and%20when%20they%20came%20out%2C%20their%20shoes%20and%20slippers%20were%20missing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20tussle%2C%20key%20issues%20like%20education%2C%20employment%2C%20roads%20and%20electricity%20have%20taken%20a%20back%20seat%20with%20each%20candidate%20trying%20to%20outdo%20the%20other%20to%20project%20himself%20as%20the%20champion%20of%20the%20tribal%20community%2C%20according%20to%20some%20non-tribal%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20area%20lacks%20industries%20and%20job%20opportunities.%20Many%20people%20from%20this%20region%20work%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20state%20of%20Gujarat.%20Women%20are%20also%20seen%20working%20in%20farms%20and%20in%20labour%20work%20in%20large%20numbers%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20non-tribal%20local%20resident%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ideology%20of%20BAP%20appears%20to%20be%20radical%20and%20could%20emerge%20as%20a%20threat%20in%20the%20time%20to%20come.%20Issues%20are%20less%20important%2C%20they%20are%20polarising%20people%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20need%20for%20the%20Congress%20to%20find%20an%20alliance%20partner%20in%20Banswara-Dungarpur%20was%20necessitated%20after%20Malviya%20-%20a%20satrap%20from%20the%20Vagad%20region%20-%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Malviya%2C%20who%20was%20made%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20twice%20in%20the%20previous%20Congress%20governments%2C%20quit%20the%20party%20after%20being%20denied%20the%20post%20of%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Congress'%20defeat%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20resigned%20as%20the%20MLA%20from%20Bagidora%20assembly%20constituency%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BAP%20--%20the%20new%20party%20from%20the%20Vagad%20region%20--%20held%20discussions%20for%20an%20alliance%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20consensus%20on%20seat%20sharing%20and%20resistance%20by%20some%20local%20Congress%20leaders%20delayed%20the%20finalisation%20of%20the%20coalition.%20On%20the%20last%20day%20of%20filing%20of%20nominations%2C%20the%20Congress%20decided%20to%20field%20Damor%20from%20Banswara-Dungarpur%20and%20Kapoor%20Singh%20from%20Bagidora%20for%20the%20bypoll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20before%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20nominations%2C%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20in%20charge%20Sukhjinder%20Singh%20Randhawa%20announced%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20party%20would%20support%20BAP%20in%20both%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20a%20rude%20shock%20for%20the%20Congress%2C%20its%20two%20candidates%20refused%20to%20withdraw%20their%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20eight%20assembly%20segments%20under%20the%20Banswara-Dungarpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20four%20MLAs%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20three%20and%20the%20BAP%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20in%20Rajasthan%20is%20contesting%20the%20elections%20as%20part%20of%20an%20alliance%20on%20two%20seats%20--%20Nagaur%20(with%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party)%20and%20Sikar%20(with%20CPI-M).%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713962820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fcd5fjuas_rajasthan-banswara-lok-sabha-seat-congress-candidate-arvind-damor_625x300_24_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-urges-voters-not-to-vote-for-its-own-candidate-in-this-rajasthan-seat-5511978%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20peculiar%20poll%20battle%20is%20on%20the%20cards%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Banswara-Dungarpur%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20in%20Rajasthan%20where%20the%20Congress%20is%20appealing%20to%20the%20people%20not%20to%20vote%20for%20its%20candidate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-urges-voters-not-to-vote-for-its-own-candidate-in-this-rajasthan-seat-5511978%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-urges-voters-not-to-vote-for-its-own-candidate-in-this-rajasthan-seat-5511978%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-urges-voters-not-to-vote-for-its-own-candidate-in-this-rajasthan-seat-5511978%