s%20and%20continue%20all%20other%20transactions%20online%20and%20offline%20without%20any%20hindrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20regulatory%20move%20will%20significantly%20impact%20the%20bank's%20customer%20acquisition%20targets%20as%20most%20of%20the%20onboardings%20happen%20online%20and%20through%20mobile%20banking%20channels.%20This%20may%20in%20turn%20affect%20its%20growth%20in%20the%20short%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20cease%20and%20desist%20order%20on%20the%20issuance%20of%20fresh%20credit%20cards%20may%20also%20severely%20hurt%20the%20bank's%20several%20co-brand%20deals%20on%20credit%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Prompted%20The%20RBI%20Crackdown%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank's%20actions%20were%20necessitated%20by%20significant%20concerns%20arising%20out%20of%20its%20IT%20examination%20of%20the%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20in%202022%20and%202023%20and%20the%20private%20bank's%20continued%20failure%20to%20address%20them%20in%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20timely%20manner%2C%20the%20official%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSerious%20deficiencies%20and%20non-compliance%20were%20observed%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20IT%20inventory%20management%2C%20patch%20and%20change%20management%2C%20user%20access%20management%2C%20vendor%20risk%20management%2C%20data%20security%20and%20data%20leak%20prevention%20strategy%2C%20business%20continuity%2C%20and%20disaster%20recovery%20rigour%20and%20drill%2C%20etc.%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20was%20found%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20non-compliant%20with%20the%20Corrective%20Action%20Plans%20issued%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20for%20the%20years%202022%20and%202023%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20subsequent%20audits%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20compliances%20submitted%20by%20the%20bank%20were%20found%20to%20be%20either%20inadequate%2C%20incorrect%20or%20not%20sustained.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bank%20is%20found%20to%20be%20materially%20deficient%20in%20building%20necessary%20operational%20resilience%20on%20account%20of%20its%20failure%20to%20build%20IT%20systems%20and%20controls%20commensurate%20with%20its%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20further%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EService%20Disruptions%20And%20Outages%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotak%20Mahindra%20Bank's%20Core%20Banking%20System%20(CBS)%20and%20its%20online%20and%20digital%20banking%20channels%20suffered%20several%20outages%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20-%20the%20most%20recent%20being%20a%20service%20disruption%20on%20April%2015%2C%20resulting%20in%20serious%20customer%20inconveniences%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20listing%20how%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20robust%20IT%20infrastructure%20and%20IT%20Risk%20Management%20framework%20affected%20customers.%20On%20April%2015%2C%20Kotak%20Bank%20customers%20could%20not%20reportedly%20access%20banking%20services%20for%20almost%2012%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20said%20it%20observed%20a%20rapid%20growth%20in%20the%20volume%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank's%20digital%20transactions%2C%20including%20through%20credit%20cards%2C%20which%20is%20further%20burdening%20the%20IT%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Reserve%20Bank%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20place%20certain%20business%20restrictions%20on%20the%20bank%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20customers%20and%20to%20prevent%20any%20possible%20prolonged%20outage%20which%20may%20seriously%20impact%20not%20only%20the%20bank's%20ability%20to%20render%20efficient%20customer%20service%20but%20also%20the%20financial%20ecosystem%20of%20digital%20banking%20and%20payment%20systems.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Will%20The%20Curbs%20Be%20Lifted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%20will%20be%20reviewed%20after%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Banks%20conducts%20an%20external%20audit%20with%20the%20R