n.%20Students%20began%20approaching%20her%20at%20school%20and%20told%20her%20that%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%20famous%20name%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20release%20of%20her%20album%20%26quot%3B1989%26quot%3B%20in%202014.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%2C%20'No%2C%20I%20don't.'%20Then%20I%20realized%20who%20she%20was.%20Now%20I'm%20a%20top%20Swiftie%20fan.%20I%20love%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20her%20namesake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019-year-old%20said%20that%20she%20was%20popular%20in%20school%20and%20never%20had%20problems%20with%20%26quot%3Bgetting%20bullied%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20in%20a%20few%20arguments%2C%20I%20got%2C%20'Shut%20up%20-%20your%20name's%20Taylor%20Swift.'%20Some%20people%20don't%20like%20her.%20But%20I%20love%20Taylor.%20That's%20life%3B%20you%20just%20move%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20she%20faces%20a%20major%20problem%20as%20employers%20think%20that%20she%20is%20not%20%26quot%3Bgenuine%26quot%3B%20when%20she%20applies%20to%20jobs%20and%20has%20a%20difficult%20time%20finding%20work.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20applying%20for%20jobs%2C%20I%20think%20I%20don't%20get%20any%20news%20back%20because%20they're%20looking%20at%20my%20name%20and%20they%20think%20it's%20a%20fake%20application%20or%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20shared.%20Additionally%2C%20this%20younger%20Taylor%20acknowledges%20that%20her%20name%20might%20be%20embarrassing%20and%20she%20has%20faced%20suspicion%20from%20medical%20professionals%2C%20dentists%2C%20retail%20employees%2C%20and%20other%20individuals.%20%26quot%3BThe%20last%20holiday%20we%20went%20on%2C%20we%20were%20approaching%20the%20gate%20when%20we%20could%20hear%20the%20air%20hostesses%20saying%2C%20'We%20can't%20believe%20her%20name%20is%20Taylor%20Swift%2C'%20And%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20passport%20checks%2C%20staff%20are%20skeptical.%20They%20say%20to%20her%2C%20'Your%20name%20is%20what%3F'%20And%20they'll%20look%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20mother%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2019-year-old%20also%20has%20issues%20showing%20her%20ID%20at%20bars%20since%20people%20are%20not%20convinced%20about%20her%20name%20and%20age%20as%20she%20%26quot%3Blooks%20so%20young%26quot%3B%20and%20shares%20a%20name%20with%20a%20famous%20personality.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'll%20get%20in%20with%20my%20ID.%20And%20then%20everybody's%20talking%20about%20my%20name%2C%20saying%2C%20'Taylor%20Swift%20is%20in%20the%20pub.'%20I%20need%20to%20show%20everybody%20my%20passport.%20I've%20been%20embarrassed%20so%20much%20because%20of%20my%20name%20that%20I%20deserve%20something%20good%20out%20of%20it.%20I%20do%20like%20my%20name%20-%20it's%20quite%20unique.%20But%20sometimes%20there%20can%20be%20embarrassing%20sides%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20youngster%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20shared%20that%20she%20is%20not%20even%20able%20to%20make%20a%20Facebook%20account%20due%20to%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20put%20her%20name%20into%20Facebook%2C%20they%20were%2C%20like%2C%20'You're%20trying%20to%20copy%20her%20name.'%20We%20sent%20them%20documents%20but%20they%20still%20said%20she%20was%20copying%20a%20celebrity's%20name%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20mother%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20self-proclaimed%20%26quot%3BSwiftie%26quot%3B%2C%20this%20teenager%20Taylor%20Swift%20acknowledges%20that%20she%20enjoys%20singing%20her%20namesake's%20songs%20at%20karaoke%20whenever%20she%20gets%20the%20chance.%20She%20even%20hopes%20to%20get%20tickets%20to%20the%20June%20Eras%20Tour%20performance%20at%20Murrayfield%20Stadium%20in%20Edinburgh.%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20Taylor%20Swift.%20I%20was%20saying%20to%20my%20pals%20if%20she%20comes%20here%2C%20I'll%20need%20to%20get%20a%20ticket%20so%20I%20can%20go%20on%20stage%20with%20her.%20I'd%20hold%20up%20a%20big%20poster%20saying%2C%20'My%20name%20is%20Taylor%20Swift.'%20I%20wanted%20tickets%2C%20but%20they%20are%20so%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2019-year-old%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A17139623400