dra%20Bank%20Limited%20(hereinafter%20referred%20to%20as%20'the%20bank')%20to%20cease%20and%20desist%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20from%20(1)%20onboarding%20of%20new%20customers%20through%20its%20online%20and%20mobile%20banking%20channels%20and%20(II)%20issuing%20fresh%20credit%20cards.%20The%20bank%20shall%2C%20however%2C%20continue%20to%20provide%20services%20to%20its%20existing%20customers%2C%20including%20its%20credit%20card%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20central%20bank%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20said%20the%20actions%20are%20based%20on%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20concerns%20arising%20out%20of%20Reserve%20Bank's%20IT%20Examination%20of%20the%20bank%20for%20the%20years%202022%20and%202023%20and%20the%20continued%20failure%20on%20part%20of%20the%20bank%20to%20address%20these%20concerns%20in%20a%20comprehensive%20and%20timely%20manner%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20there%20were%20%26quot%3Bserious%20deficiencies%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20way%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20manages%20its%20IT%20inventory%20and%20secures%20its%20data.%C2%A0%26quot%3BSerious%20deficiencies%20and%20non-compliances%20were%20observed%20in%20the%20areas%20of%20IT%20inventory%20management%2C%20patch%20and%20change%20management%2C%20user%20access%20management%2C%20vendor%20risk%20management%2C%20data%20security%20and%20data%20leak%20prevention%20strategy%2C%20business%20continuity%20and%20disaster%20recovery%20rigour%20and%20drill%2C%20etc.%20For%20two%20consecutive%20years%2C%20the%20bank%20was%20assessed%20to%20be%20deficient%20in%20its%20IT%20Risk%20and%20Information%20Security%20Governance%2C%20contrary%20to%20requirements%20under%20Regulatory%20guidelines%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20subsequent%20assessments%2C%20the%20bank%20was%20found%20to%20be%20significantly%20non-compliant%20with%20the%20Corrective%20Action%20Plans%20issued%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20for%20the%20years%202022%20and%202023%2C%20as%20the%20compliances%20submitted%20by%20the%20bank%20were%20found%20to%20be%20either%20inadequate%2C%20incorrect%20or%20not%20sustained%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20noted%20that%20due%20to%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20robust%20IT%20infrastructure%2C%20the%20bank's%20digital%20banking%20channels%20have%20suffered%20frequent%20outages%20and%20inconvenienced%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20robust%20IT%20infrastructure%20and%20IT%20Risk%20Management%20framework%2C%20the%20bank's%20Core%20Banking%20System%20(CBS)%20and%20its%20online%20and%20digital%20banking%20channels%20have%20suffered%20frequent%20and%20significant%20outages%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20recent%20one%20being%20a%20service%20disruption%20on%20April%2015%2C%202024%2C%20resulting%20in%20serious%20customer%20inconveniences.%20The%20bank%20is%20found%20to%20be%20materially%20deficient%20in%20building%20necessary%20operational%20resilience%20on%20account%20of%20its%20failure%20to%20build%20IT%20systems%20and%20controls%20commensurate%20with%20its%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20has%20been%20in%20continuous%20high-level%20engagement%20with%20the%20bank%20on%20all%20these%20concerns%20with%20a%20view%20to%20strengthening%20its%20IT%20resilience%2C%20but%20the%20outcomes%20have%20been%20far%20from%20satisfactory.%20It%20is%20also%20observed%20that%2C%20of%20late%2C%20there%20has%20been%20rapid%20growth%20in%20the%20volume%20of%20the%20bank's%20digital%20transactions%2C%20including%20transactions%20pertaining%20to%20credit%20cards%2C%20which%20is%20building%20further%20load%20on%20the%20IT%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20central%20bank%20has%20said%20it%20has%20decided%20to%20place%20some%20curbs%20on%20the%20bank%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20customers.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Reserve%20Bank%2C%20therefore%2C%20has%20decided%20to%20place%20certain%20business%20restrictions%20on%20the%20bank%20as%20mentioned%20above%2C%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20customers%20and%20to%20prevent%20any%20possible%20prolonged%20outage%20which%20may%20seriously%20impact%20not%20only%20the%20bank's%20ability%20to%20render%20efficient%20customer%20service%20but%20also%20the%20financial%20ecosystem%20of%20digital%20banking%20and%20payment%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curbs%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20said%2C%20will%20be%20review%20after%20an%20audit%20and%20corrective%20steps.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20restrictions%20now%20being%20imposed%20will%20be%20reviewed%20upon%20completion%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20external%20audit%20to%20be%20commissioned%20by%20the%20bank%20with%20the%20prior%20approval%20of%20RBI%2C%20and%20remediation%20of%20all%20deficiencies%20that%20may%20be%20pointed%20out%20in%20the%20external%20audit%20as%20well%20as%20the%20observations%20contained%20in%20the%20RBI%20Inspections%2C%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20Reserve%20Bank.%20Further%2C%20these%20restrictions%20are%20without%20prejudice%20to%20any%20other%20regulatory%2C%20supervisory%20or%20enforcement%20action%20that%20may%20be%20initiated%20against%20the%20bank%20by%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKotak%20Mahindra's%20journey%20started%20in%201985%20when%20Uday%20Kotak%20founded%20Kotak%20Capital%20Management%20Finance%20as%20an%20investment%20and%20financial%20services%20company.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20Anand%20Mahindra%20and%20his%20father%20Harish%20Mahindra%20invested%20in%20the%20company%2C%20and%20it%20was%20renamed%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Finance%20Ltd.%20received%20banking%20licence%20from%20the%20RBI%20and%20became%20the%20first%20non-banking%20finance%20company%20in%20India%20to%C2%A0convert%20into%20a%20bank.%C2%A0The%20bank%20currently%20offers%20services%20ranging%20from%20commercial%20banking%20to%20stock%20broking%20to%20mutual%20funds%20to%20insurance%20and%20investment%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20on%20December%2031%20last%20year%2C%20the%20bank%20has%204.8%20crore%20customers%2C%201%2C869%20branches%20and%203%2C239%20ATMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713958320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fv64402r8_kotak-mahindra-bank_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-barred-by-rbi-from-onboarding-new-online-customers-5512868%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Citing%20data%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20has%20barred%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20from%20onboarding%20new%20customers%20online%20and%20issuing%20new%20credit%20cards%20with%20immediate%20effect.%20The%20bank%20can%2C%20however%2C%20continue%20to%20serve%20its%20customers%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-barred-by-rbi-from-onboarding-new-online-customers-5512868%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-barred-by-rbi-from-onboarding-new-online-customers-5512868%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-barred-by-rbi-from-onboarding-new-online-customers-5512868%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Wife%2C%20Gets%20Clean%20Chit%20In%20Rs%2025%2C000-Crore%20'Scam'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20reprieve%20for%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20wife%20of%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20NDA%20candidate%20for%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20given%20her%20a%20clean%20chit%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%2025%2C000-crore%20cooperative%20bank%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20closure%20report%20filed%20in%20January%20-%20details%20of%20which%20have%20now%20emerged%20-%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Cooperative%20Bank%20(MSCB)%20case%2C%20has%20said%20that%20no%20criminal%20offence%20is%20made%20out%20in%20the%20transactions%20allegedly%20linked%20to%20Ms%20Pawar%20and%20her%20husband.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Pawar%20will%20be%20contesting%20from%20the%20Baramati%20seat%2C%20a%20bastion%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20against%20his%20daughter%20Supriya%20Sule%2C%20who%20is%20also%20her%20sister-in-law.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20of%20the%20report%20has%20given%20more%20ammunition%20to%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20has%20consistently%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20central%20agencies%20and%20police%20forces%20against%20leaders%20opposed%20to%20it%20and%20either%20going%20slow%20on%20the%20investigation%20or%20giving%20them%20a%20clean%20chit%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20align%20with%20the%20saffron%20party.%20The%20opposition%20parties%20call%20this%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bwashing%20machine%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjit%20Pawar%20had%20joined%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20faction)%20and%20taken%20oath%20as%20a%20Maharashtra%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20after%20breaking%20the%20NCP%2C%20formed%20by%20his%20uncle%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW's%20closure%20report%20states%20that%20the%20bank%20did%20not%20suffer%20any%20loss%20in%20the%20process%20of%20sanctioning%20loans%20to%2C%20or%20the%20sale%20of%2C%20the%20Jarandeshwar%20Sugar%20Mill%2C%20which%20is%20linked%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20had%20resigned%20from%20the%20post%20of%20director%20of%20Jai%20Agrotech%20in%202008%20and%2C%20two%20years%20later%2C%20%C2%A0the%20company%20gave%20Rs%2020.25%20crore%20to%20Jarandeshwar%20Sugar%20Mill.%20The%20mill%20was%20then%20bought%20by%20a%20firm%20called%20Guru%20Commodity%20in%20an%20auction%20for%20Rs%2065.75%20crore%20but%20given%20on%20lease%20again%20to%20a%20company%20in%20which%20relatives%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20including%20Rajendra%20Ghadge%2C%20were%20directors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuru%20Commodity%20was%20given%20Rs%2065.53%20crore%20by%20this%20company%20as%20rent.%20The%20EOW%20said%20it%20found%20nothing%20illegal%20in%20these%20transactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWashing%20Powder%20Jibe%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clean%20chit%20has%20come%20under%20fire%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%20which%20is%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20state.%20Party%20leader%20Anand%20Dubey%20said%20the%20police's%20action%20is%20proof%20that%20opposition's%20washing%20machine%20claim%20is%20completely%20justified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Hindi%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSunetra%20Pawar%20has%20been%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20in%20a%20case%20in%20which%20an%20allegation%20of%20a%20Rs%2025%2C000-crore%20scam%20was%20levelled%20by%20none%20other%20than%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20who%20had%20called%20the%20entire%20family%20corrupt.%20This%20proves%20that%20the%20opposition's%20claim%20that%20leaders%20are%20cleaned%20of%20all%20allegations%20after%20being%20washed%20with%20washing%20powder%20is%20completely%20true.%20Every%20leader%20who%20was%20accused%20by%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20given%20a%20clean%20chit%20after%20switching%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20former%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BCases%2C%20however%2C%20go%20on%20against%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20they%20are%20arrested%20even%20if%20they%20are%20chief%20ministers.%20But%20if%20they%20align%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20are%20made%20ministers%2C%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20and%20given%20Lok%20Sabha%20tickets.%20And%2C%20when%20we%20point%20this%20out%20and%20oppose%20it%2C%20the%20BJP%20gets%20agitated%20and%20worried.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20during%20the%20third%20phase%20on%20May%207.%20Results%20will%20be%20out%20on%20June%204.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713958260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffu8b7gl_sunetra-pawar_625x300_18_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunetra-pawar-wife-of-ajit-pawar-gets-clean-chit-in-rs-25-000-crore-scam-5513139%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20reprieve%20for%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20wife%20of%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20NDA%20candidate%20for%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20has%20given%20her%20a%20clean%20chit%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%2025%2C000-crore%20cooperative%20bank%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunetra-pawar-wife-of-ajit-pawar-gets-clean-chit-in-rs-25-000-crore-scam-5513139%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunetra-pawar-wife-of-ajit-pawar-gets-clean-chit-in-rs-25-000-crore-scam-5513139%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsunetra-pawar-wife-of-ajit-pawar-gets-clean-chit-in-rs-25-000-crore-scam-5513139%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emirates%20Calls%20Girl's%20Father%20At%204%20am%20After%20She%20Misses%20Flight%3A%20%26quot%3BWell%20Done%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man