%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flily-gladstone-leonardo-dicaprio-titanic-vhs-allowance-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELily%20Gladstone%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20really%20happened%20by%20the%20river.%20Godfrey%20did%20not%20assist%20the%20authorities%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20teenage%20girls%20and%20one%20teenage%20boy%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20attack%20on%20Virk%2C%20which%20started%20when%20ringleader%20Nicole%20Cook%20put%20out%20a%20cigarette%20on%20Virk's%20face.%20After%20Virk%20escaped%2C%20Warren%20Glowatski%20and%20Kelly%20Ellard%20followed%20her%20and%20continued%20beating%20her.%20Then%2C%20they%20drowned%20her%20in%20a%20body%20of%20water%20known%20as%20the%20Gorge%20Waterway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20girls%2C%20who%20were%20nicknamed%20the%20%26quot%3BShoreline%20Six%2C%26quot%3B%20were%20given%20a%20variety%20of%20sentences%20for%20aggravated%20assault.%20But%20Glowatski%20and%20Ellard%2C%20who%20are%20played%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feuphoria-season-2-fun-facts-behind-the-scenes-details-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJavon%20Walton%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Izzy%20G%20in%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Bridge%2C%26quot%3B%20were%20tried%20as%20adults%20and%20convicted%20of%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20where%20Glowatski%20and%20Ellard%20are%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlowatski%20was%20granted%20parole%20in%202010%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Javon%20Walton%20as%20Warren%20Glowatski%20in%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Bridge.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66228ecb10c6b0cde5f12ff4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJavon%20Walton%20as%20Warren%20Glowatski%20in%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Bridge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHulu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGlowatski%20was%2016%20when%20he%20took%20part%20in%20Virk's%20murder%2C%20and%20a%20year%20later%2C%20in%201998%2C%20he%20was%20convicted%20of%20second-degree%20murder%20and%20given%20a%20life%20sentence%20with%20the%20possibility%20of%20parole%20after%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20serving%20his%20sentence%2C%20Glowatski%20took%20part%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frestorative-justice-philadelphia-healing-futures-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestorative%20justice%20programs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20discovered%20that%20he%20had%20M%C3%A9tis%20indigenous%20Canadian%20heritage%2C%20and%20worked%20with%20elders%20to%20use%20cultural%20techniques%20to%20take%20responsibility%20for%20the%20crime%2C%20including%20apologizing%20to%20Virk's%20parents%20in%20a%20healing%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECTV%20reported%20in%202006%20that%20Glowatski%20hugged%20Virk's%20parents%20when%20he%20was%20granted%20unescorted%20temporary%20passes%20in%202006%2C%20aged%2025.%20Virk's%20mother%2C%20Suman%20Virk%2C%20wished%20him%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20thankful%20and%20grateful%20you%20have%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20your%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20here%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20forward.%20I%20hope%20you%20stick%20to%20your%20path%20and%20prove%20that%20you%20have%20learned%20from%20your%20experiences%20and%20will%20truly%20love%20and%20respect%20others%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20later%20granted%20full%20parole%20at%20a%20hearing%20in%202010%2C%20where%20he%20told%20the%20parole%20board%20how%20much%20he%20regretted%20his%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20hated%20myself.%20I%20think%20that%20night%20I%20turned%20that%20hate%20outward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20co-accused%20held%20her%20head%20under%20water%20and%20I%20didn't%20stop%20it.%20I%20didn't%20set%20out%20in%20the%20morning%20to%20take%20part%20in%20a%20murder.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEllard%20is%20still%20in%20prison%20but%20has%20been%20granted%20day%20parole%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221749%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Izzy%20G%20as%20Kelly%20Ellard%20in%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Bridge.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66228f1420b15f0ff4299ab7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIzzy%20G%20as%20Kelly%20Ellard%20in%20%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Bridge.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EHulu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEllard%20was%20convicted%20of%20second-degree%20murder%20in%202000%2C%20which%20was%20later%20overturned%20after%20an%20appeal.%20After%20her%20second%20trial%20was%20declared%20a%20mistrial%20in%202004%2C%20Ellard%20was%20given%20a%20life%20sentence%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fcanada%2Fbritish-columbia%2Freena-virk-kelly-ellard-day-parole-1.3564981%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202016%20that%20she%20was%20denied%20day%20parole%20in%202016%20because%20the%20parole%20board%20didn't%20think%20she%20had%20taken%20responsibility%20for%20killing%20Virk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Storey%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20board%2C%20said%20at%20the%20time%3A%20%26quot%3BShe%20still%20seems%20to%20be%20minimizing%20many%20aspects%20of%20the%20offence.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20more%20evidence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllard%2C%20who%20now%20goes%20by%20Kerry%20Sim%2C%20was%20later%20granted%20day%20parole%20in%202017%2C%20and%20in%202020%20was%20allowed%20to%20live%20away%20from%20prison%20for%20up%20to%20five%20days.%20She%20has%20two%20children%20with%20an%20ex-partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vicnews.com%2Fnews%2Fkelly-ellard-declines-chance-for-full-parole-says-shes-not-ready-100249%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVictoria%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202022%20tha