ble-rousers%20this%20election%2C%20like%20Nalin%20Kateel%20in%20Dakshina%20Kannada%2C%20Pragya%20Singh%20Thakur%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20and%20even%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20in%20South%20Delhi.%20The%20BJP%20perhaps%20felt%20that%20leaders%20who%20were%20needed%20to%20mobilise%20Hindu%20sentiments%20ahead%20of%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20were%20not%20required%20any%20more.%20With%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20finally%20becoming%20a%20reality%2C%20aggressive%20Hindu%20posturing%20was%20not%20necessary%2C%20the%20party%20may%20have%20believed.%20But%2C%20right%20when%20people%20thought%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20taking%20on%20a%20new%2C%20mellow%20avatar%2C%20it%20sprung%20a%20surprise.%20Through%20a%20single%20speech%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20managed%20to%20build%20an%20electoral%20narrative%20centred%20around%20Hindus%20allegedly%20being%20under%20threat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-controversy-bjp-vs-congress-congress-manifesto-has-congress-promised-wealth-redistribution-in-manifesto-a-fact-check-5511606%5C%22%3Eif%20the%20Congress%20comes%20to%20power%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttacking%20The%20Manifesto%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20narrative%20was%20not%20built%20off%20a%20one-time%20mention.%20PM%20Modi%20followed%20up%20his%20Banswara%20speech%20with%20a%20similar%20one%20the%20next%20day%20in%20Western%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Aligarh%2C%20where%20he%20railed%20against%20the%20Congress%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20party%20planned%20to%20%26quot%3Bseize%20the%20wealth%20of%20Hindu%20women%20to%20redistribute%20among%20minorities%26quot%3B.%20The%20latter%20rushed%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmust-act-congress-to-election-commission-over-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-remark-5497957%5C%22%3Edemand%20action%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20PM%2C%20but%20nothing%20deterred%20him.%20For%20the%20third%20consecutive%20day%2C%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Tonk-Sawai%20Madhopur%2C%20he%20again%20warned%20voters%20about%20the%20perils%20of%20voting%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi's%20plan%20of%20attack%20clearly%20hinged%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-manifesto-biggest-loss-for-people-less-than-25-years-of-age-pm-modi-5447313%5C%22%3ECongress's%20manifesto%20and%20poll%20promises%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20included%20a%20yearly%20sum%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%20to%20women.%20Parts%20of%20the%20manifesto%2C%20read%20along%20with%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20disputed%20remarks%20in%202006%2C%20were%20interpreted%20by%20PM%20Modi%20to%20infer%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20came%20to%20power%2C%20it%20would%20redistribute%20wealth%20among%20those%20%26quot%3Bwith%20more%20children%26quot%3B%20(by%20which%20he%20evidently%20meant%20Muslims).%20He%20also%20cited%20the%20%26quot%3Burban%20naxal%20mindset%26quot%3B%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20advisors%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20Congress%20would%20not%20spare%20even%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-election-2024-my-mother-sacrificed-her-mangalsutra-for-india-priyanka-gandhi-amid-row-5507644%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emangalsutra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20%26quot%3Bmothers%20and%20sisters%26quot%3B.%20He%20based%20his%20claims%20on%20the%20Congress%20manifesto's%20promise%20of%20a%20nationwide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-wealth-redistribution-congress-manifesto-pm-modi-sam-pitroda-have-not-said-rahul-gandhi-amid-wealth-redistribution-row-5511829%5C%22%3Esocio-economic%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20caste%20census.%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20the%20data%2C%20we%20will%20strengthen%20the%20agenda%20for%20affirmative%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20document.%20However%2C%20though%20there%20were%20reports%20that%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20Rahul%20had%20said%20the%20Congress%20would%20redistribute%20wealth%20amongst%20minorities%2C%20the%20party%20has%20now%20rejected%20making%20any%20such%20claims.%20The%20manifesto%20has%20no%20mention%20of%20any%20such%20%26quot%3Bre-distribution%26quot%3B%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20On%20Backfoot%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%20though%2C%20the%20result%20of%20PM%20Modi's%20speeches%20is%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20on%20the%20defensive%20over%20its%20manifesto.%20The%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20which%20maintains%20that%20it%20respects%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20(PMO)%2C%20has%20sought%20action%20from%20the%20ECI%2C%20contending%20that%20the%20'%3Cem%3Emangalsutra%3C%2Fem%3E'%20imagery%20can%20inflame%20communal%20sentiments.%20%26quot%3BThe%20%3Cem%3EShehzada%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5Bprince%5D%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20the%20Congress%20says%20that%20if%20their%20government%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20they%20will%20investigate%20who%20earns%20how%20much%2C%20who%20has%20how%20many%20properties...%20Our%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20have%20gold.%20It%20is%20'%3Cem%3Estreedhan%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20it%20is%20considered%20sacred%2C%20the%20law%20also%20protects%20it.%20Now%20these%20people's%20eyes%20are%20on%20the%20'%3Cem%3Emangalsutra%3C%2Fem%3E'%20of%20women.%20Their%20intention%20is%20to%20steal%20the%20gold%20of%20mothers%20and%20sisters...%20This%20is%20Maovadi%20thinking%2C%20this%20is%20the%20thinking%20of%20communists%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20had%20said%20in%20his%20speech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20Opposition's%20demands%20for%20action%20against%20the%20PM%2C%20however%2C%20what's%20interesting%20is%20that%20many%20BJP%20leaders%20themselves%20are%20not%20comfortable%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20Modi%20talking%20about%20the%20alleged%20threat%20to%20Hindus.%20%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20such%20misgivings%20about%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%20should%20not%20have%20been%20articulated%20by%20PM%20Modi%20himself.%20It%20is%20best%20left%20to%20rabble-rousers.%20%C2%A0It%20should%20have%20been%20left%20to%20our%20second-line%20or%20third-line%20leaders%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Karnataka%20BJP%20MP%20said.%20But%20then%2C%20given%20how%20the%20party%20has%20dispensed%20with%20most%20of%20such%20hardline%20leaders%2C%20who%20could%20possibly%20be%20flagging%20these%20issues%20for%20the%20BJP%3F%20That's%20probably%20why%20PM%20Modi%20chose%20to%20himself%20make%20such%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Tough%20First%20Phase%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20section%20within%20the%20BJP%20also%20feels%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20utterances%20could%20be%20linked%20to%20the%20experience%20of%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20polling%20on%20April%2019%2C%20which%2C%20many%20say%2C%20may%20not%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20BJP's%20favour.%20It%20is%20also%20likely%20that%20this%20time%2C%20many%20party%20cadres%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20do%20much%20heavy-lifting%2C%20feeling%20let%20down%20by%20the%20choice%20of%20candidates%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20tickets%20have%20been%20given%20to%20many%20who%20just%20crossed%20over%20from%20the%20Congress%20or%20the%20AAP%2C%20or%20other%20opposition%20parties.%20Naveen%20Jindal%20being%20fielded%20from%20Kurukshetra%20and%20Ashok%20Chavan%20being%20accommodated%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20are%20a%20few%20examples.%20These%20leaders%20came%20with%20baggage%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20and%20see%20the%20impact%20of%20Chavan's%20induction%20in%20Marathwada%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20BJP%20leader%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20RSS%20leader%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20says%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20objective%20could%20be%20to%20push%20people%20to%20vote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20crossovers%20may%20not%20affect%20voters%2C%20they%20may%20all%20still%20have%20faith%20in%20Modiji%20and%20vote%20for%20him.%20But%20then%20again%2C%20this%20campaign%20of%20'400%20%3Cem%3Epaar%3C%2Fem%3E'%20%5BMission%20400%5D%20may%20prove%20to%20be%20counterproductive%20as%20voters%20may%20not%20be%20motivated%20enough%20to%20come%20to%20the%20polling%20booth%20if%20they%20feel%20PM%20Modi%20is%20sure%20to%20be%20elected%2C%20with%20or%20without%20them.%20It%20is%20quite%20likely%20that%20Modi%20may%20have%20raked%20up%20the%20Hindu%20cause%20to%20motivate%20people%20to%20vote...%20In%20fact%20when%20Modi%20raised%20the%20bias%20against%20Hindus%20in%20the%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20BJP%20chief%20J.P.%20Nadda%20simultaneously%20spoke%20about%20the%20'love%20jihad'%20issue%20in%20Congress-ruled%20Karnataka.%20He%20visited%20the%20family%20of%20Neha%20Hiremath%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20Congress%20corporator%2C%20who%20was%20a%20victim.%20With%20elections%20underway%2C%20the%20party%20picks%20up%20issues%20close%20to%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20election%20year%20though%2C%20mobilising%20Hindu%20votes%20with%20such%20speeches%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20Faustian%20bargain%20for%20PM%20Modi%2C%20one%20that%20may%20cost%20him%20the%20goodwill%20earned%20among%20the%20country's%20Muslims%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20through%20his%20good%20governance%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Lakshmi%20Iyer%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20been%20covering%20politics%20for%20four%20decades%20in%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20Mumbai.%20She%20is%20on%20X%20%40%3C%2Fem%3Eliyer%3Cem%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20views%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713952560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F7b5cvgnk_pm-modi_640x480_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fpm-modi-mangalsutra-row-a-faustian-bargain-for-bjp-5512276%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mobilising%20Hindu%20votes%20with%20such%20speeches%20could%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20Faustian%20bargain%20for%20PM%20Modi%2C%20one%20that%20may%20cost%20him%20the%20goodwill%20earned%20among%20the%20count