on%20the%20land%20years%20before%20we%20found%20it%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20stays%20there%20for%20a%20long%20time%20to%20come.%20It%20passes%20right%20through%20the%20master%20bedroom%20of%20the%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInspiration%20comes%20from%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocated%20in%20Wayanad%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Estate%20Paathiri%20is%20the%20perfect%20place%20to%20seek%20solace.%20While%20the%20world%20bustles%20with%20noises%2C%20here%20you%20will%20wake%20up%20to%20the%20sounds%20of%20birds%20chirping%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20and%20inspiration%20for%20nature%20being%20a%20recurring%20theme%20in%20George%E2%80%99s%20work%20goes%20back%20to%20his%20childhood.%20Born%20in%20Coorg%2C%20George%20says%20he%20grew%20up%20around%20nature.%20%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F197644%2Flifestyle-order-ooty-chocolates-online-handmade-organic-empower-women-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20school%20in%20Ooty%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20covered%20with%20forest%20all%20around.%20It%20was%20this%20proximity%20to%20nature%20that%20made%20me%20feel%20one%20with%20it.%20Now%20I%20believe%20that%20there%20is%20no%20material%20or%20design%20that%20can%20be%20superior%20to%20what%20nature%20has%20to%20offer%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20the%20place%20a%20natural%20oasis%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20our%20earlier%20projects%20we%20have%20always%20ensured%20that%20the%20place%20is%20full%20of%20trees%20and%20greenery%20but%20this%20particular%20one%20is%20unique.%20Its%20focal%20point%20is%20a%20tree%20itself%2C%20which%20is%20very%20fascinating.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20green%20haven%20is%20a%20home%20for%20the%20current%20owners%20of%20the%20