-attack-hit-iranian-air-defence-radar-satellite-pictures-suggest-13121459%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Tests%20Your%20Mental%20Strength%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%202%20Indians%20Swam%20For%20Over%2010%20Hrs%20Covering%2032%20Km%20In%20Indian%20Ocean%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20a%20sponsored%20article.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2014%20April%2C%202024%2C%20at%205%20am%2C%20the%20coast%20of%20Talaimannar%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20was%20a%20bustling%20hub%20of%20activity.%20A%20team%20was%20busy%20checking%20arrangements%20and%20making%20sure%20all%20the%20documents%20and%20safety%20measures%20were%20in%20place.%20Amidst%20this%20flurry%20of%20activity%2C%20two%20men%20sat%20calm%20and%20composed%2C%20as%20they%20were%20about%20to%20attempt%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20challenges%20of%20their%20life%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313790%2Fharyana-duo-startup-seniorworld-helps-the-elderly-travel-across-the-world%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eswimming%20across%20the%20Palk%20Strait%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20swim%20in%20the%20open%20ocean%20started%20shortly%20after%205%20am%2C%20and%20Bharat%20Sachdeva%20and%20Shaaswat%20Sharma%20swam%20across%20the%20challenging%2032%20km%20stretch%20near%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20in%2010%20hours%2030%20minutes%2C%20non-stop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20encountered%20choppy%20waters%20and%20tough%20weather%2C%20but%20nothing%20deterred%20the%20two%20swimmers%20from%20their%20target.%20They%20battled%20sea%20sickness%2C%20rough%20waters%2C%20sunburn%2C%20and%20many%20mental%20challenges%20to%20finish%20this%20extraordinary%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20the%20physical%20barriers%2C%20it%20was%20a%20battle%20of%20the%20mind%20and%20emotions%2C%20share%20the%20two%20swimmers.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20time%20we%20felt%20sick%2C%20or%20had%20to%20swim%20over%20the%20choppy%20waters%2C%20we%20just%20thought%20of%20our%20goal%2C%20and%20that%20kept%20us%20going.%20It%20was%20emotionally%20and%20physically%20draining%2C%20but%20the%20bigger%20picture%20kept%20us%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharat%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20two%20athletes%2C%20this%20swimming%20expedition%20goes%20beyond%20challenging%20their%20limits%2C%20it%20aims%20to%20promote%20adventure%20sports%20and%20open%20swimming%20in%20India%2C%20raise%20awareness%20about%20water%20safety%20and%20prevent%20drowning%20incidents%20while%20fostering%20universal%20brotherhood%20and%20friendship%20among%20neighbouring%20countries.%20These%20goals%20of%20creating%20more%20athletes%20and%20swimmers%20in%20India%20kept%20the%20duo%20fighting%20till%20they%20reached%20Dhanushkodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOver%20900%20days%20of%20preparation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharat%20(40)%20is%20a%20health%20and%20wellness%20consultant%2C%20an%20international%20swimmer%2C%20and%20an%20Ironman%20triathlete.%20He%20has%20trained%20champions%20like%20M%20C%20Mary%20Kom%2C%20Amit%20Panghal%2C%20Vikas%20Krishan%20Yadav%20and%20more%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20high-performance%20coaching%20unit%20with%20the%20Indian%20Boxing%20Team%20preparing%20for%20the%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharat%20and%20Shaaswat%20swam%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-17-at-17.23.18-1-min-1713871081-scaled.jpeg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2