%20wanted%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20global%20map%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20idea%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20to%20foster%20positive%20relationships%20between%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20they%20started%20preparations%20in%20earnest%20almost%20three%20years%20back%2C%20says%20the%20swimmer.%20They%20christened%20the%20expedition%20the%20%E2%80%98Ram%20Setu%20Swimming%20Expedition%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20started%20planning%20and%20practising%20for%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20prepared%20in%20different%20water%20and%20weather%20conditions%20with%20an%20experienced%20crew%20guiding%20them%2C%20and%20training%20them%20on%20water%20safety%20and%20preventing%20accidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20their%20practice%20was%20indoors%2C%20swimming%20in%20the%20open%20waters%20was%20a%20completely%20different%20ballgame%2C%20concedes%20Bharat%2C%20which%20accentuates%20the%20need%20for%20better%20infrastructure%20and%20investment%20to%20promote%20such%20sports%20in%20the%20country.%20He%20adds%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286757%2Fpara-swimmer-spina-bifida-breaks-asian-record-niranjan-mukundan-surgeries-medals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-water%20swimming%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20a%20very%20popular%20sport%20in%20India%2C%20and%20needs%20to%20be%20promoted.%20And%20to%20also%20bring%20this%20to%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20set%20an%20example%20by%20accomplishing%20this%20incredible%20feat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20efforts%20will%20be%20successful%20when%20we%20see%20more%20young%20talent%20from%20India%20opting%20for%20swimming%20and%20representing%20the%20country%20at%20prestigious%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bharat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20undertake%20this%20initiative%2C%20the%20swimmers%20received%20permissions%20from%20relevant%20authorities%20like