ic%20farming%20%E2%80%93%20an%20innovative%20and%20efficient%20way%20to%20grow%20crops%20without%20needing%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20soil-less%20farming%20technique%20piqued%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Barabanki%20district%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIsrael%20has%20been%20extremely%20progressive%20in%20farming%20despite%20having%20a%20dry%20climate%2C%20limited%20water%20resources%2C%20and%20high%20population%20density%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20what%20they%20grew%20in%20an%20acre%20of%20land%2C%20they%20were%20able%20to%20export%20it%20to%20several%20countries.%20I%20wondered%2C%20if%20they%20were%20exporting%20produce%20from%20just%20one%20acre%2C%20why%20was%20I%20lagging%20behind%20despite%20owning%2010%20acres%20of%20land%3F%20I%20was%20not%20able%20to%20sell%20my%20produce%20even%20to%20the%20next%20village%2C%20let%20alone%20to%20the%20other%20countries%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDheeraj%20was%20so%20fascinated%20by%20the%20technique%20that%20he%20went%20on%20to%20watch%20hundreds%20of%20related%20videos%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F265317%2Futtar-pradesh-hydroponics-farm-home-grows-vegetables-fruits-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehydroponics%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Israel.%20His%20obsession%20led%20him%20to%20adopt%20the%20practice%20in%20his%20village%20Meenapur%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20which%20is%20well-known%20for%20cultivating%20traditional%20crops%20like%20wheat%2C%20maize%20and%20rice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A