dds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Dheeraj%2C%20hydroponics%20farming%20seemed%20a%20panacea%20for%20all%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20went%20to%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20to%20undertake%20training%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336600%2Ftech-nursery-hydroponics-aeroponics-farming-ratlam-brothers-arbind-ravindra-dhakad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDhakad%20Brothers%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20learn%20the%20hydroponics%20method%20of%20cultivation.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20hydroponics%20farming%2C%20you%20give%20nutrients%20to%20plants%20via%20water.%20A%20crop%20requires%2013%20kinds%20of%20nutrients%20including%20primary%20nutrients%20like%20nitrogen%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20and%20potassium%2C%20secondary%20nutrients%20like%20calcium%2C%20sulphur%2C%20and%20magnesium%2C%20and%20tertiary%20nutrients%20like%20iron%2C%20zinc%2C%20manganese%2C%20copper%2C%20boron%2C%20molybdenum%2C%20and%20chlorine.%20These%20elements%20act%20as%20an%20essential%20catalyst%20for%20plant%20growth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20knew%20the%20technique%20to%20give%20these%20nutrients%20via%20water%2C%20I%20did%20not%20know%20the%20ratio%20in%20which%20these%20elements%20were%20required%20to%20be%20given%20to%20the%20crop.%20The%20training%20helped%20me%20learn%20the%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Within%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-3-1-1713533903.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fupl