e%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20maintenance%20of%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20two%20months%2C%20Dheeraj%20was%20able%20to%20harvest%205%20tonnes%20of%20strawberries%20and%20earned%20an%20income%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20the%20same%20period.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20method%20is%20far%20better%20than%20conventional%20farming.%20With%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20got%20five%20times%20more%20production%20in%20hydroponics%20compared%20to%20open-land%20farming%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20tasks%20farmers%20should%20be%20mindful%20of%20while%20adopting%20this%20method%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20need%20to%20monitor%20the%20hydroponics%20farm%20at%20least%20once%20every%20day.%20The%20strawberries%20are%20heavily%20attacked%20by%20pests%20and%20fungus.%20In%20land-based%20farming%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20spray%20chemical%20pesticides%20indiscriminately.%20But%20in%20hydroponics%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20cut%20chemical%20inputs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Early%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-2-1-1713533802-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347855%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEarly%20this%20year%2C%20Dheeraj%20made%20sales%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%20within%20two%20months%20by%20cultivating%20strawberries%20hydroponically.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%2C%20he%20prepared%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338548%2Fmaharashtra-farmer-earns-huge-profits-by-growing-strawberry-farm-near-pune%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunique%20fungicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20curd.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20one%20litre%20of%20curd%2C%20add%2050%20grams%20of%20copper%20wires%20or%20a%20copper%20%3Cem%3Elota%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spherical%20vessel).%20Keep%20the%20content%20for%20at%20least%2015%C2%A0%20days%20until%20the%20content%20becomes%20completely%20blue.%20Take%202%20ml%20of%20this%20mixture%20and%20dilute%20it%20in%201%20litre%20of%20water.%20Spray%20the%20diluted%20content%20on%20crops%20once%20every%20week%20throughout%20the%20season.%20This%20tackles%20fungi%20attack%20and%20gives%20a%20good%20yield%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20am%20extremely%20happy%20to%20reap%20benefits%20by%20adopting%20this%20new%20technique%2C%20initially%20I%20made%20some%20mistakes%20in%20getting%20good%20nutrients%20from%20the%20market.%20I%20got%20misled%20into%20buying%20nutrients%20from%20fraud%20companies.%20This%20delayed%20my%20production%20by%201.5%20months.%20But%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20earn%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20in%20the%20next%20season%20from%20the%20same%20setup%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dheeraj%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20cultivating%20red%20and%20yellow%20varieties%20of%20capsicum%20on%20the%20hydroponics%20setup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20his%20example%2C%20Dheeraj%20advises%20other%20farmers%20to%20explore%20hydroponics%20farming.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20technique%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%20any%20untutored%20farmer%20can%20reap%20handsome%20profits%20with%20hydroponics%20like%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%20All%20photos%3A%20Dheeraj%20Verma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713767578000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fstrawberry-1-1713533722.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347819%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Encouraged%20by%20the%20soil-less%20farming%20technique%20used%20in%20Israel%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Dheeraj%20Verma%20turned%20to%20cultivating%20strawberries%20using%20hydroponics.%20He%20earned%20Rs%203%20lakh%20in%20just%20two%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347819%2Fstrawberry-farming-in-uttar-pradesh-hydroponics-farm-in-barabanki-earns-farmer-lakhs%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Architect%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Beehive%E2%80%99%20Cooling%20System%20is%20Affordable%20%26amp%3B%20Reduces%20Electricity%20Bills%20by%2065%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20scorching%20summer%20heat%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20energy%20peaks%2C%20increasing%20our%20electricity%20bills.%20While%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioners%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20artificial%20coolers%20not%20only%20drain%20our%20pockets%20but%20also%20harm%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Monish%20Siripurapu%20has%20come%20up%20with%20an%20affordable%20natural%20air%20cooler%20that%20not%20only%20keeps%20you%20cool%20in%20summer%20but%20also%20helps%20cut%20down%20on%20electricity%20bills%20by%20up%20to%2065%20percent!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20has%20designed%20CoolAnt%20which%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20nature%20to%20keep%20spaces%20cool%20and%20comfortable.%20Interestingly%2C%20its%20terracotta%20design%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20efficient%20cooling%20techniques%20of%20beehives%20and%20brings%20together%20sustainability%20and%20functionality%20in%20one%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20utilises%20terracotta%20cones%20arranged%20in%20a%20beehive%20pattern.%20Water%20is%20allowed%20to%20flow%20over%20the%20terracotta%20cones%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20natural%20cooling%20agent%2C%20absorbing%20heat%20from%20the%20surroundings.%20It%20then%20uses%20the%20process%20of%20evaporative%20cooling%20to%20release%20a%20gentle%2C%20refreshing%20breeze%20into%20the%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20re-adaptation%20of%20traditional%20methods%2C%20combining%20ancient%20systems%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187517%2Flifestyle-eco-friendly-cooling-solution-without-ac-sustainable-homes-architect-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodern%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20are%20opening%20buildings%20to%20nature%20instead%20of%20building%20installations%20for%20conventional%20urban%20structures%20that%20shut%20their%20inhabitants%20into%20these%20closed%20boxes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20observed%20that%20this%20structure%20can%20comfortably%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20up%20to%2030%20degrees%20Celsius.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20from%2045-47%20to%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%20because%20the%20water%20temperature%20was%2026-27%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%2020