%20Indian%20language%20fonts%20by%20ITF.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20font%20is%20the%20Kohinoor%20series%20designed%20by%20Satya.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20Kohinoor%2C%20there%20was%20no%20font%20that%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246205%2F83-yo-kerala-school-dropout-creates-unique-dictionary-in-4-south-indian-languages-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20all%20Indian%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20an%20airport%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20we%20need%20signage%20in%20three%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20Gujarati.%20Fonts%20in%20a%20family%20are%20aesthetically%20consistent.%20Apple%20has%20licensed%20the%20Kohinoor%20family.%20If%20you%20get%20a%20message%20in%20Hindi%20or%20Gujarati%20from%20an%20Apple%20device%2C%20the%20font%20will%20be%20from%20our%20Kohinoor%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20Kohinoor%20font%20family%20is%20on%20display%20permanently%20in%20London%E2%80%99s%20The%20Design%20Museum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20inspirations%20and%20innovations%20driving%20ITF%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20ITF%20faced%20was%20the%20scarcity%20of%20skilled%20type%20designers%20in%20India.%20Students%20and%20interns%20were%20trained%20and%20added%20to%20the%20team.%20Today.%20the%20team%20of%2025%20members%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20hurdle%20was%20cultivating%20a%20market%20for%20fonts.%20More%20people%2C%20including%20students%2C%20are%20now%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20quality%20fonts%2C%20recognising%20their%20impact%20on%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20communication%20and%20branding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3