o%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20gave%20his%20own%20example%20of%20what%20he%20did%20when%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20his%20name%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Choly%20pdf%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20message%20to%20everyone%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20is%3A%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20give%20up.%20Never.%20Be%20proud%20that%20you%20have%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitin%20recalls%20sitting%20in%20his%20Gurugram%20house%2C%20heart%20pounding%2C%20as%20he%20impatiently%20checked%20the%20UPSC%20website%20multiple%20times%20to%20see%20if%20the%20result%20was%20out.%20Finally%2C%20as%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20he%20downloaded%20the%20million-dollar%20final%20list%20and%20checked%20it%20thrice%20for%20his%20name.%20He%20even%20did%20%E2%80%98Ctrl%20%2B%20F%E2%80%99%20with%20trembling%20hands%2C%20confirming%20that%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20numb%20and%20confused%2C%20and%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20only%20me%3F%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20candid%20post%20that%20now%20has%20over%201.25%20lakh%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20came%20to%20the%20bureaucrat%E2%80%99s%20rescue%20that%20day.%20Jitin%20met%20his%20friend%20and%20received%20an%20important%20life%20lesson%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20everyone%20in%20a%20difficult%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20happens%2C%20happens%20for%20good%20only.%20We%20can%20only%20give%20our%20100%25.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20ahead%20%E2%80%94%20one%20to%20be%20depressed%20and%20do%20nothing%2C%20other%20to%20immediately%20bounce%20back%20after%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20and%20do%20what%20all%20past%20selected%20candidates%20have%20done%20who%20faced%20rejections%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20and%20author%20chose%20the%20second%20option%20and%20was%20selected%20in%20the%20next%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20necessary%20for%20everyone%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20same%20path%20as%20there%20are%20many%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F345398%2Ffree-upsc-coaching-mentorship-programme-delhi-former-irs-officer-ravi-kapoor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecareer%20options%20beyond%20UPSC%3C%2Fa%3E.%20To%20such%20students%2C%20he%20advises%20taking%20a%20break%20and%20then%20figuring%20out%20a%20future%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetter%20things%20are%20waiting%20for%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%20bureaucrat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20the%20entire%20post%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-twitter%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFor%20the%20ones%20who%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%20at%20home%20in%20Gurgaon%20and%20got%20to%20know%20that%20result%20will%20come%20today.%20I%20checked%20UPSC%20website%20after%20every%2015%20minutes.%20Finally%20the%20link%20came%20and%20i%20downloaded%20the%20pdf.%20Heart%20was%20pumping.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20opened%20it%2C%20started%20scrolling%20and%20the%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jitin%20Yadav%20(%40Jitin_IAS)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJitin_IAS%2Fstatus%2F1780459875652264273%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Feature%20Image%20Courtesy%20Jitin%20Yadav%2FX%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713432518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D347611%22%2C%22summary%22%3